P(\vec{\partial})=\sum_{\abs{\vec{\alpha}}\le m}C_{\vec{\alpha}}\vec{\partial}^{\vec{\alpha}}\equiv\sum_{\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}\alpha_{i}\right)\le m}C_{\alpha_{1}\cdots\alpha_{n}}\pdv[\alpha_{1}]{x_{1}}\cdots\pdv[\alpha_{n}]{x_{n}}
